{"type":"message","id":"edc4bd50","parentId":"b69bc4f1","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:25.365Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_268230d4dfea5f51af33421d332e3bd3\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_268230d4dfea5f51af33421d332e3bd3\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 16:14 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_268230d4dfea5f51af33421d332e3bd3\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_268230d4dfea5f51af33421d332e3bd3\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_268230d4dfea5f51af33421d332e3bd3\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71]\nou_268230d4dfea5f51af33421d332e3bd3: @_all 理解md文件，介绍自己的信息，工作职责及对公司业务的理解。"}],"timestamp":1776759265365}}
{"type":"message","id":"621a8d94","parentId":"edc4bd50","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:30.840Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to understand the markdown files, introduce myself, my work responsibilities, and my understanding of the company's business. Let me look at what I already have from the project context.\n\nI already have AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, USER.md, IDENTITY.md, TOOLS.md, and BOOTSTRAP.md loaded in the Project Context above. Let me work with those.\n\nKey info:\n- Name: 数据诊断分析虾（7号）\n- Role: AI数据分析助手\n- Company: 美域高 (appears to be a company dealing with qualification/permit services like ICP许可证)\n\n\n- Responsibilities include building and maintaining the business dashboard with customer acquisition metrics, sales conversion rates, delivery timelines, and service satisfaction scores; providing weekly diagnosis reports that identify trends and recommend actions; and escalating data anomalies to relevant stakeholders within two hours. The organization has a numbered structure ranging from general management down through specialized roles in branding, lead generation, short video marketing, private operations, and sales tiers.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！📊 我是**数据诊断分析虾（7号）**，简单自我介绍下：\n\n---\n\n我是公司的数据分析和业务诊断角色。核心价值就是从数据里挖出\"利润增长点\"和\"风险爆点\"。\n\n**三个核心职责：**\n\n1️⃣ **建仪表盘** — 维护《美域高作战仪表盘》，盯四个维度：\n获客端看各渠道线索成本和转化效率；销售端盯4A/4B的咨询→报价→签约转化率；交付端关注5A/5B的办理周期和按时率；服务端跟踪客户满意度和复购转介绍\n\n2️⃣ **做归因** — 每周一输出《业务诊断周报》，不光报数字，还要说清楚为什么异常、该干什么\n\n3️⃣ **发预警** — 发现重大数据异常，2小时内直接@责任人+抄送0号老板\n\n**对公司业务的理解：** 美域高是一家资质代办服务公司（ICP许可证等），商业模式是靠运营和内容获取线索，经过销售漏斗转化为客户，最后由交付团队办完交给客户。我们的链条比较长，从内容获客到售后维系至少跨越8个岗位，任何一个环节的数据波动都可能影响最终营收，所以我需要横向拉通看数据，帮助各位虾子知道哪里卡了、哪里该发力。\n\n以后大家有数据需求直接@我就行 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":20464,"output":721,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21185,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776759265366,"responseId":"chatcmpl-cd0f43ac-0fd9-9fc8-a71f-3a1fb23dff3c"}}
